latestIgtvVideos.title: Lockdown Essentials Tray
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We all are in the process of adapting the “New Normal”

I told myself during this time that I’ll rest more, sleep more, take care of myself and my mental health. I love music. I love working out, running, and curating healthy recipes and that's been my favourite way to destress.

I put together these lockdown essentials tray to avoid making kitchen trips again and again. While we need to have a healthy relationship with food, in such times, all of us are bound to indulge in binge eating and boredom eating. It’s alright to keep a tab on what you eat. You would not even realise the hidden calories that you are consuming. Eat mindfully and stay safe.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Surya Namaskar or Sun Salutation
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Surya Namaskar or Sun Salutation is a sequence of 12 powerful yoga poses. Besides being a great cardiovascular workout, Surya Namaskar is also known to have an immensely positive impact on the body and mind.

Surya Namaskar is best done early morning on an empty stomach. Each round of Sun Salutation consists of two sets, and each set is composed of 12 yoga poses. 
Before you start giving your expert opinions, let me tell you that you might find several versions on how to practice Sun Salutation. 
However, it is advisable to stick to one particular version and practice it regularly for best results.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Vegan Curried Chickpeas Salad
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The fact that ordering food is just a click away these days, I have slowly realised the importance of eating home cooked meals especially when I am not traveling. 
It’s time to take back our kitchens and our homes. 
The solution to weight loss and healthy eating is in our shopping carts, our refrigerators, our cupboards and on our dining room tables. 
All you need to do is choose ingredients, shop for real food and cook from scratch. I do not mind spending on healthy or expensive ingredients for salads, etc. Sharing the recipe of Vegan Curried Chickpeas salad in this video. Feel free to ask any questions in the comment section. Skip feta if you are vegan.
